FBIS4-16753 "drsov076_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Dismisses Nizhniy Novgorod Representative Yeltsin Dismisses Nizhniy Novgorod Representative LD1904145194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 19 Apr 94 LD1904145194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] We have received Boris Yeltsin's decree relieving Boris Nemtsov of his post as the Russian president's representative in Nizhniy Novgorod Oblast at the latter's request. Yevgeniy Khristyaninov has been appointed as presidential representative in the oblast by a decree issued by Yeltsin.
